data.description: Welcome to 4135 Coventry Lane! *UNDER 230k in SWA SCHOOLS* Discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality in this ranch-style home, ideally situated in the heart of Southwest Fort Wayne. 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with an oversized master bedroom with an ensuite bathroom! Located in the award winning Southwest schools district, this home is a sure to impress. The highlight of this home is the spacious kitchen, boasting a very large island, high-quality cabinets, and an abundance of counter and cabinet space. Modern upgrades include new flooring, and the updated kitchen appliances that are included, ensuring a hassle-free move-in experience. The square, privacy fenced in backyard makes for easy maintenance and great privacy. The attached two-car garage, provides secure parking and additional storage. 2 minutes from Coventry, 3 minutes from Jorgensen YMCA, 7 minutes from Jefferson Point, 10 minutes to downtown. Priced under $250,000, do not miss this home!
